1
00:00:18,980 --> 00:00:24,420
♪It's a sordid story that you've made♪

2
00:00:26,700 --> 00:00:32,700
♪Up to fill my mind with doubts and pain♪

3
00:00:34,780 --> 00:00:40,220
♪Blood I shed, and tears I wept,
are you satisfied?♪

4
00:00:40,220 --> 00:00:42,540
♪Enjoying what's mine♪

5
00:00:42,540 --> 00:00:49,500
♪Have you found a way
to bury guilt and shame♪

6
00:00:50,540 --> 00:00:55,020
♪I'm coming back to life♪

7
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:58,700
♪Through the seven gates of death♪

8
00:00:58,700 --> 00:01:02,820
♪I'm coming back survived♪

9
00:01:02,820 --> 00:01:06,580
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

10
00:01:06,580 --> 00:01:10,820
♪I'm taking back what's mine♪

11
00:01:10,820 --> 00:01:15,340
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

12
00:01:15,340 --> 00:01:19,060
♪Lay it to waste♪

13
00:01:19,060 --> 00:01:22,940
♪Til the day my kingdom is reclaimed♪

14
00:01:38,260 --> 00:01:42,540
=Her Blaze=

15
00:01:43,260 --> 00:01:45,820
=Episode 22=

16
00:01:47,000 --> 00:01:47,840
Little Genius.

17
00:01:48,000 --> 00:01:49,000
I'm impressed.

18
00:01:49,560 --> 00:01:51,400
Who would've thought
a good guy like you

19
00:01:51,400 --> 00:01:52,760
actually had an ace up her sleeve?

20
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:55,200
Of course good people have leverage.

21
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:58,079
The real question is
how they choose to use it

22
00:01:58,359 --> 00:01:59,239
and on whom.

23
00:02:00,599 --> 00:02:01,920
So, let me ask you,

24
00:02:01,920 --> 00:02:02,719
Mr. Pengyu.

25
00:02:03,359 --> 00:02:04,680
If you actually win,

26
00:02:05,159 --> 00:02:06,920
what's your next move?

27
00:02:11,319 --> 00:02:12,800
To the rest of the world,

28
00:02:15,479 --> 00:02:16,840
you're probably just out for blood.

29
00:02:18,439 --> 00:02:19,879
But when I look at you,

30
00:02:20,160 --> 00:02:21,319
it's more than a vendetta.

31
00:02:22,719 --> 00:02:24,639
You have other plans, don't you?

32
00:02:27,840 --> 00:02:28,879
Can you get to the point?

33
00:02:28,879 --> 00:02:30,000
I have no idea

34
00:02:30,000 --> 00:02:31,639
what you're talking about.

35
00:02:34,120 --> 00:02:35,080
Let's talk

36
00:02:36,560 --> 00:02:37,879
about that four percent.

37
00:02:38,840 --> 00:02:39,639
Perfect.

38
00:02:40,879 --> 00:02:42,520
I much prefer this pace.

39
00:02:43,400 --> 00:02:44,199
Let's hear it.

40
00:02:44,879 --> 00:02:46,280
What's your price

41
00:02:46,280 --> 00:02:48,000
for that four percent stake?

42
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:50,240
My condition is very simple.

43
00:02:50,840 --> 00:02:51,680
I want

44
00:02:51,680 --> 00:02:53,039
the snack street back in business.

45
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,039
That's it?

46
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:02,439
That's it.

47
00:03:07,599 --> 00:03:08,919
This four percent

48
00:03:08,960 --> 00:03:11,240
holds the fate
of Lysen Group, Baiye Group,

49
00:03:11,360 --> 00:03:12,879
and Bosi Real Estate in its balance.

50
00:03:12,879 --> 00:03:14,159
And you're just handing it over

51
00:03:14,159 --> 00:03:15,120
just like that?

52
00:03:15,560 --> 00:03:16,520
Just like that.

53
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,639
Remember what I told you?

54
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:30,599
I do think you're a good person.

55
00:03:32,199 --> 00:03:33,680
It's easy to be the villain.

56
00:03:34,599 --> 00:03:36,319
But admitting you're a good person

57
00:03:37,520 --> 00:03:38,800
seems to be impossible for you.

58
00:03:40,199 --> 00:03:40,960
But admitting

59
00:03:40,960 --> 00:03:42,159
you're a good person

60
00:03:43,159 --> 00:03:44,180
seems impossible for you.

61
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,199
Because you are one.

62
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,159
I've told you already.

63
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:53,759
I'm no saint.

64
00:03:53,800 --> 00:03:54,719
Just sign the contract.

65
00:04:12,240 --> 00:04:13,039
Attention, everyone.

66
00:04:13,040 --> 00:04:15,230
The battle for Bosi Real Estate equity
has taken a sudden turn.

67
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,680
Yinyu Technology announced today

68
00:04:16,680 --> 00:04:18,740
the acquisition
of four percent of the circulating shares.

69
00:04:18,759 --> 00:04:21,279
They have seized the lead with a total
of twenty-five percent.

70
00:04:21,360 --> 00:04:22,839
They now hold a narrow advantage

71
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:23,879
over the alliance between

72
00:04:23,879 --> 00:04:24,959
Yang Jinwan and Baiye Group,

73
00:04:24,959 --> 00:04:26,110
who hold twenty-four percent.

74
00:04:26,120 --> 00:04:28,160
Lysen Group follows
with twenty-three percent.

75
00:04:28,759 --> 00:04:29,839
The seller

76
00:04:29,879 --> 00:04:30,639
in this transaction

77
00:04:30,639 --> 00:04:32,120
has not yet been disclosed.

78
00:04:32,240 --> 00:04:32,920
This shift

79
00:04:32,920 --> 00:04:33,759
leaves Jiang Dongchao

80
00:04:33,759 --> 00:04:34,680
who had the best chance

81
00:04:34,680 --> 00:04:36,560
at a distinct disadvantage.

82
00:05:21,959 --> 00:05:23,839
I heard the snack street is reopening.

83
00:05:25,319 --> 00:05:25,920
Yuci.

84
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,000
Your dream is finally coming true.

85
00:05:32,839 --> 00:05:33,639
Chen Mo.

86
00:05:35,319 --> 00:05:36,240
I must thank you.

87
00:05:40,360 --> 00:05:41,199
I really mean it.

88
00:05:43,240 --> 00:05:44,920
I'm so glad I met you.

89
00:05:48,319 --> 00:05:49,639
If it weren't for you,

90
00:05:51,160 --> 00:05:51,920
I'd probably

91
00:05:51,920 --> 00:05:53,519
still be trapped in the dark.

92
00:05:54,560 --> 00:05:55,759
Consumed by anger,

93
00:05:56,199 --> 00:05:57,399
bitterness,

94
00:05:57,720 --> 00:05:58,920
and an endless obsession.

95
00:06:00,879 --> 00:06:02,800
But because you came into my life,

96
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:06,319
I feel like...

97
00:06:10,240 --> 00:06:12,120
I can finally step out into the light.

98
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:26,439
Yuci.

99
00:06:28,399 --> 00:06:28,879
Remember

100
00:06:28,879 --> 00:06:30,079
that story I told you?

101
00:06:32,240 --> 00:06:33,240
About the little boy.

102
00:06:34,000 --> 00:06:35,199
After losing his parents,

103
00:06:35,199 --> 00:06:36,240
he was convinced

104
00:06:36,240 --> 00:06:37,360
he could make it on his own.

105
00:06:39,279 --> 00:06:40,560
But after more than a decade,

106
00:06:40,959 --> 00:06:42,040
he realized

107
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,439
that the path was just too lonely.

108
00:06:48,079 --> 00:06:49,600
So he wanted to do everything he could

109
00:06:50,120 --> 00:06:51,240
to help others.

110
00:06:52,319 --> 00:06:53,279
To stop them

111
00:06:55,199 --> 00:06:56,920
from struggling in pain the way he did.

112
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:00,759
He wasn't sure

113
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:01,560
how to go about it.

114
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,199
But he didn't want

115
00:07:04,199 --> 00:07:05,319
the woman he loves

116
00:07:09,319 --> 00:07:11,120
to walk down that lonely road by herself.

117
00:07:23,519 --> 00:07:24,839
Everytime I pictured you

118
00:07:24,839 --> 00:07:25,879
in that hospital bed,

119
00:07:25,879 --> 00:07:26,959
it terrified me.

120
00:07:29,160 --> 00:07:29,800
I know

121
00:07:29,800 --> 00:07:31,319
you have things you need to finish.

122
00:07:33,680 --> 00:07:34,759
But I want to

123
00:07:34,759 --> 00:07:35,920
be right there with you.

124
00:07:37,620 --> 00:07:41,820
♪Waiting in the crowd
for just one glance♪

125
00:07:42,300 --> 00:07:46,820
♪No matter how long♪

126
00:07:47,360 --> 00:07:49,000
Did you know that the sunset only lasts

127
00:07:49,000 --> 00:07:49,959
six hundred seconds?

128
00:07:50,839 --> 00:07:51,639
I didn't.

129
00:07:54,199 --> 00:07:55,439
I hope that I can spend those

130
00:07:58,680 --> 00:07:59,759
six hundred seconds

131
00:07:59,759 --> 00:08:01,079
with you every day.

132
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:06,160
To cherish every single moment.

133
00:08:07,540 --> 00:08:13,260
♪You're the moonlight of my soul♪

134
00:08:13,260 --> 00:08:19,660
♪I wish to become your final harbor♪

135
00:08:19,660 --> 00:08:26,620
♪Sleepless and tireless,
let me silently wait for you♪

136
00:08:27,540 --> 00:08:32,900
♪You're the moonlight of my soul♪

137
00:08:32,900 --> 00:08:39,140
♪I wish I could watch
every view with you♪

138
00:08:39,140 --> 00:08:44,540
♪Oh, but sadly I'm only a friend♪

139
00:08:44,540 --> 00:08:50,900
♪You're the moonlight of my soul♪

140
00:08:50,900 --> 00:08:57,340
♪I wish I could walk with you
till the end of time♪

141
00:08:57,340 --> 00:09:04,380
♪Nothing more, I need
to stay by your side♪

142
00:09:17,039 --> 00:09:17,840
Yuci.

143
00:09:18,759 --> 00:09:20,440
Can you get off work a bit early today?

144
00:09:21,240 --> 00:09:22,039
Why? What's up?

145
00:09:22,840 --> 00:09:23,960
Nothing, I was just asking.

146
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,159
What are you up to?

147
00:09:28,440 --> 00:09:30,159
Are you trying to surprise me?

148
00:09:32,120 --> 00:09:33,559
Surprise? What surprise?

149
00:09:33,559 --> 00:09:34,320
I'm not.

150
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:40,039
Listen.

151
00:09:40,520 --> 00:09:41,399
I don't do birthdays.

152
00:09:41,399 --> 00:09:42,519
So don't bother.

153
00:09:42,759 --> 00:09:43,879
Why not?

154
00:09:44,390 --> 00:09:45,399
You skipped them before.

155
00:09:45,399 --> 00:09:46,990
So we're making up for every single one.

156
00:09:47,919 --> 00:09:48,799
Why?

157
00:09:49,639 --> 00:09:50,639
I just want you to be

158
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:53,000
happy, safe, and loved

159
00:09:53,399 --> 00:09:55,200
every single day of every year.

160
00:09:58,080 --> 00:09:59,800
Whatever others have,
we should have too.

161
00:10:06,840 --> 00:10:07,639
Hello.

162
00:10:10,200 --> 00:10:11,799
I need to talk to him for a second.

163
00:10:11,799 --> 00:10:12,440
Sure.

164
00:10:12,639 --> 00:10:13,440
It's just work.

165
00:10:16,240 --> 00:10:17,279
Come on, everyone!

166
00:10:17,279 --> 00:10:18,240
Have some watermelon.

167
00:10:18,240 --> 00:10:19,240
Help yourselves!

168
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:22,279
Come and get it!

169
00:10:22,480 --> 00:10:24,759
Thank you, Mr. Pengyu,
for keeping your word.

170
00:10:25,240 --> 00:10:26,559
No, I should be thanking you.

171
00:10:26,960 --> 00:10:29,039
If it weren't
for that four percent stake,

172
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:30,759
I never could've turned the tables.

173
00:10:34,399 --> 00:10:35,200
Little Genius.

174
00:10:36,639 --> 00:10:37,440
Have you considered

175
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:39,120
the consequences of doing this?

176
00:10:39,240 --> 00:10:40,159
I have.

177
00:10:43,399 --> 00:10:44,279
Thanks, man.

178
00:10:44,279 --> 00:10:45,399
Good job, everyone.

179
00:10:46,039 --> 00:10:46,840
But I have things

180
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,879
I absolutely have to do.

181
00:10:48,919 --> 00:10:49,720
Cool.

182
00:10:52,700 --> 00:10:54,480
Ever thought about allying
with Lysen Group?

183
00:11:00,639 --> 00:11:01,440
Little Genius.

184
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:04,360
If that's what you're really after,

185
00:11:04,960 --> 00:11:06,200
then take your four percent

186
00:11:06,200 --> 00:11:07,519
and get the hell out of here.

187
00:11:07,519 --> 00:11:09,240
I'd rather die than ever

188
00:11:09,240 --> 00:11:10,480
cooperate with Jiang Dongchao.

189
00:11:10,480 --> 00:11:11,279
I said Lysen Group,

190
00:11:11,279 --> 00:11:12,279
not Jiang Dongchao.

191
00:11:13,399 --> 00:11:14,559
Do you follow me?

192
00:11:19,279 --> 00:11:20,080
Think about it.

193
00:11:21,120 --> 00:11:22,360
In this takeover battle,

194
00:11:22,360 --> 00:11:24,399
if Lysen Group loses
to Yinyu Technology,

195
00:11:25,399 --> 00:11:26,480
Jiang Dongchao,

196
00:11:27,350 --> 00:11:28,480
will bear the responsibility.

197
00:11:29,279 --> 00:11:31,519
He was the one who insisted

198
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,200
on setting up the fund.

199
00:11:34,240 --> 00:11:35,720
So what you're saying is

200
00:11:37,679 --> 00:11:39,399
now is the perfect time

201
00:11:39,639 --> 00:11:41,440
to force Mr. Jiang out of Lysen Group?

202
00:11:42,679 --> 00:11:43,639
For you,

203
00:11:44,679 --> 00:11:46,159
this is the chance of a lifetime.

204
00:11:53,960 --> 00:11:55,480
If it means getting Jiang Dongchao

205
00:11:55,480 --> 00:11:56,559
out of Lysen Group,

206
00:11:56,810 --> 00:11:58,679
then I'm definitely
open to working with you.

207
00:11:59,559 --> 00:12:01,600
Or rather, with Li Wancheng.

208
00:12:08,360 --> 00:12:09,960
Now that the snack street is reopening,

209
00:12:09,960 --> 00:12:11,880
we have to make sure
we maintain our standards.

210
00:12:12,080 --> 00:12:14,390
Many regular customers
have been dying for us to come back.

211
00:12:15,120 --> 00:12:16,679
Exactly.

212
00:12:16,679 --> 00:12:17,720
Mr. Chen is right.

213
00:12:19,440 --> 00:12:21,720
Work hard and do a good job, all right?

214
00:12:21,720 --> 00:12:22,879
Anyway, a huge thanks

215
00:12:23,159 --> 00:12:24,039
to Dr. Chen.

216
00:12:24,759 --> 00:12:26,320
And of course, to Yuci.

217
00:12:31,879 --> 00:12:33,440
Xian Pengyu's last move

218
00:12:34,519 --> 00:12:36,080
came out of nowhere.

219
00:12:38,799 --> 00:12:39,799
Aren't you curious

220
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:43,159
who gave him that four percent?

221
00:12:44,159 --> 00:12:45,559
I don't even have to guess.

222
00:12:46,279 --> 00:12:47,679
It was Rao Yuci.

223
00:12:48,720 --> 00:12:50,399
She must know

224
00:12:50,600 --> 00:12:52,840
that I was the one
behind closing the snack street.

225
00:12:52,840 --> 00:12:54,440
I was targeting her.

226
00:12:54,799 --> 00:12:56,840
So if the lights are back
on at the snack street,

227
00:12:57,240 --> 00:12:59,159
it's definitely her doing.

228
00:13:00,000 --> 00:13:01,559
Everyone thinks

229
00:13:02,399 --> 00:13:03,919
Rao Yuci is a genius.

230
00:13:04,399 --> 00:13:06,159
But I think she's a lunatic.

231
00:13:07,000 --> 00:13:09,600
Yuci and I are two sides
of the same coin.

232
00:13:09,799 --> 00:13:11,440
Whatever she can envision and achieve,

233
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:13,159
I can too.

234
00:13:13,159 --> 00:13:15,039
I can go where she wouldn't dare.

235
00:13:16,320 --> 00:13:17,120
Grandmother.

236
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:19,919
Where that four percent came from

237
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:20,840
doesn't matter.

238
00:13:21,000 --> 00:13:21,720
What matters

239
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:23,320
is whether Jiang Dongchao knows.

240
00:13:24,080 --> 00:13:25,480
If he finds out

241
00:13:25,480 --> 00:13:27,360
that Rao Yuci backstabbed him,

242
00:13:27,600 --> 00:13:29,159
how do you think he'll react?

243
00:13:30,679 --> 00:13:31,759
Tell me,

244
00:13:32,320 --> 00:13:33,639
what are you planning?

245
00:13:34,480 --> 00:13:35,159
Weren't we

246
00:13:35,159 --> 00:13:36,919
supposed to cooperate with him?

247
00:13:37,360 --> 00:13:39,039
This information will be
the perfect gift.

248
00:13:51,820 --> 00:13:53,820
(Harmony)

249
00:13:54,679 --> 00:13:55,480
Ms. Bai.

250
00:13:56,000 --> 00:13:56,759
Didn't you promise

251
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:58,360
not to interfere with the takeover?

252
00:13:58,660 --> 00:13:59,919
Why have you changed your mind?

253
00:13:59,919 --> 00:14:01,360
Did I do something wrong?

254
00:14:03,410 --> 00:14:04,840
Dongchao, you're overthinking this.

255
00:14:09,000 --> 00:14:11,240
I've always wanted
to collaborate with you.

256
00:14:11,480 --> 00:14:12,759
If I had

257
00:14:12,759 --> 00:14:14,279
announced my support too early,

258
00:14:14,279 --> 00:14:16,200
what would have happened
if Sir Yang found out?

259
00:14:16,200 --> 00:14:17,679
He'd be furious.

260
00:14:18,399 --> 00:14:20,000
That wouldn't have helped

261
00:14:20,000 --> 00:14:22,039
stabilize the situation at all.

262
00:14:22,879 --> 00:14:26,320
So, Bosi Real Estate
and Baiye Group joined forces first.

263
00:14:26,679 --> 00:14:28,679
Then, once we add your stake,

264
00:14:29,120 --> 00:14:29,919
the advantage

265
00:14:29,919 --> 00:14:31,320
shifts completely.

266
00:14:31,320 --> 00:14:32,440
Everything will be

267
00:14:32,440 --> 00:14:33,840
under our control.

268
00:14:34,480 --> 00:14:36,679
More importantly, you should know

269
00:14:37,679 --> 00:14:39,720
where Xian Pengyu's four percent

270
00:14:39,879 --> 00:14:41,159
actually came from.

271
00:14:41,240 --> 00:14:42,240
Who gave him the stake?

272
00:14:46,320 --> 00:14:47,879
I have a special gift for you today.

273
00:14:50,279 --> 00:14:51,080
Liangliang.

274
00:15:03,759 --> 00:15:04,639
Mr. Jiang.

275
00:15:08,120 --> 00:15:09,039
Thank you, Mr. Jiang,

276
00:15:09,039 --> 00:15:10,399
for everything you've said to me.

277
00:15:11,360 --> 00:15:12,919
It made me rethink

278
00:15:13,279 --> 00:15:15,080
the direction of my life.

279
00:15:19,360 --> 00:15:20,960
Xian Pengyu's four percent stake

280
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:21,960
in Bosi Real Estate

281
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,919
originated from a fund in Hong Kong, China

282
00:15:25,159 --> 00:15:27,240
called the Cryptex Fund.

283
00:15:28,000 --> 00:15:29,480
The person behind this fund

284
00:15:29,480 --> 00:15:30,600
is Wu Zhice.

285
00:15:31,279 --> 00:15:33,399
(Founder: Wu Zhice)
Some people call him "Master."

286
00:15:34,279 --> 00:15:35,320
He's also the founder

287
00:15:35,320 --> 00:15:36,919
(Investee Name)
of the Xinkang Treatment Center.

288
00:15:37,679 --> 00:15:40,639
And Rao Yuci happens
to be very close with him.

289
00:15:44,480 --> 00:15:45,759
Not only is she

290
00:15:47,039 --> 00:15:49,000
responsible for Muran's death,

291
00:15:50,279 --> 00:15:52,080
but she's been playing you for a fool.

292
00:15:53,960 --> 00:15:56,120
I remember you once told me that

293
00:15:56,759 --> 00:15:58,080
I was too clever for my own good.

294
00:15:58,639 --> 00:16:00,720
Thinking I could see through everything,

295
00:16:00,720 --> 00:16:02,200
dictate every plan,

296
00:16:02,240 --> 00:16:03,559
and manipulate everyone.

297
00:16:04,039 --> 00:16:05,519
Yet I had no idea

298
00:16:05,879 --> 00:16:07,879
who was lurking in the shadows.

299
00:16:08,679 --> 00:16:09,480
Bai Liangliang.

300
00:16:10,480 --> 00:16:11,600
Did you really think

301
00:16:11,600 --> 00:16:13,360
you were the smartest person
in this world?

302
00:16:13,360 --> 00:16:15,120
That you see through everything,
lay out every plan,

303
00:16:15,120 --> 00:16:16,220
and pull everyone's strings?

304
00:16:17,600 --> 00:16:19,080
But everyone is clever here.

305
00:16:20,440 --> 00:16:21,840
Your "best friend", Rao Yuci

306
00:16:24,080 --> 00:16:25,120
is far smarter than you.

307
00:16:34,039 --> 00:16:34,840
Today,

308
00:16:36,960 --> 00:16:38,159
history repeats itself.

309
00:16:39,320 --> 00:16:40,200
Mr. Jiang,

310
00:16:40,919 --> 00:16:43,639
those words apply to you as well.

311
00:16:46,159 --> 00:16:47,360
Rao Yuci engineered

312
00:16:47,360 --> 00:16:48,519
all of this.

313
00:16:49,039 --> 00:16:50,320
It's not just me.

314
00:16:50,639 --> 00:16:52,519
You were part of her plan, too.

315
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,360
Mr. Jiang,

316
00:16:55,039 --> 00:16:56,240
you're nothing more than

317
00:16:56,960 --> 00:16:58,519
another pawn being played.

318
00:17:49,350 --> 00:17:51,160
You always say
I'm just talking about ideals.

319
00:17:52,119 --> 00:17:53,599
But I will make sure you see

320
00:17:54,079 --> 00:17:55,559
that it's more than just talk.

321
00:17:55,860 --> 00:18:00,660
(Lysen Group 23%,
Yinyu Technology 19%)

322
00:18:18,620 --> 00:18:21,340
(Li Wancheng)

323
00:18:21,340 --> 00:18:25,240
(Official's Mansion)

324
00:18:25,240 --> 00:18:26,039
Mr. Li.

325
00:18:26,559 --> 00:18:27,960
Since you've invited me here today,

326
00:18:28,079 --> 00:18:29,480
please, don't hold anything back.

327
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,200
Whatever's on your mind,

328
00:18:31,720 --> 00:18:32,440
we should be able

329
00:18:32,440 --> 00:18:33,799
to speak openly and honestly.

330
00:18:34,440 --> 00:18:35,359
Given the way

331
00:18:35,359 --> 00:18:36,960
the takeover has developed,

332
00:18:38,279 --> 00:18:40,119
I really should have given
you a full update.

333
00:18:41,160 --> 00:18:42,039
I knew

334
00:18:42,519 --> 00:18:43,599
I wasn't wrong about you.

335
00:18:44,240 --> 00:18:45,039
Dongchao.

336
00:18:47,079 --> 00:18:48,519
You truly understand me well.

337
00:18:50,319 --> 00:18:53,200
Since the founding of Lysen Group,

338
00:18:53,680 --> 00:18:55,920
I've weathered countless storms.

339
00:18:57,480 --> 00:18:59,039
Protecting this legacy

340
00:18:59,680 --> 00:19:00,480
hasn't been easy.

341
00:19:01,359 --> 00:19:04,039
So, when you set out
to acquire Bosi Real Estate,

342
00:19:04,519 --> 00:19:05,880
despite the immense risks,

343
00:19:06,559 --> 00:19:07,799
I didn't stand in your way.

344
00:19:08,119 --> 00:19:09,000
Because I knew

345
00:19:09,000 --> 00:19:10,119
you were just like me.

346
00:19:10,359 --> 00:19:11,279
You were hoping

347
00:19:11,839 --> 00:19:13,559
this acquisition would give

348
00:19:14,880 --> 00:19:15,720
Lysen Group

349
00:19:16,279 --> 00:19:18,119
the chance to truly leap forward.

350
00:19:20,119 --> 00:19:21,400
I'm grateful

351
00:19:22,200 --> 00:19:23,720
for your understanding, Mr. Li.

352
00:19:26,039 --> 00:19:28,480
But with the way things stand now,

353
00:19:30,119 --> 00:19:31,440
I'm in a bit of a tough position.

354
00:19:32,759 --> 00:19:33,599
Think about it.

355
00:19:34,160 --> 00:19:36,079
You stood before all the shareholders

356
00:19:36,559 --> 00:19:37,400
and gave your word.

357
00:19:37,799 --> 00:19:39,240
Doesn't establishing a Bosi Fund

358
00:19:39,680 --> 00:19:41,440
mean you're committed

359
00:19:41,759 --> 00:19:43,039
to seeing this acquisition of

360
00:19:43,039 --> 00:19:44,119
Bosi Real Estate through?

361
00:19:44,599 --> 00:19:45,440
But now...

362
00:19:48,900 --> 00:19:50,119
The shareholders are watching.

363
00:19:50,119 --> 00:19:51,559
How am I supposed to face them?

364
00:19:52,279 --> 00:19:54,160
You've put me in an impossible position.

365
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,400
How about this...

366
00:19:58,559 --> 00:19:59,359
Look,

367
00:20:01,839 --> 00:20:02,720
for the time being,

368
00:20:04,190 --> 00:20:05,160
why don't you step down?

369
00:20:07,319 --> 00:20:08,839
When the time is right in the future,

370
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,359
I'll personally invite you back.

371
00:20:13,079 --> 00:20:15,359
Besides, I'll provide you
with a sum of money.

372
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,039
A dedicated grant.

373
00:20:17,880 --> 00:20:19,000
Thank you, Mr. Li.

374
00:20:20,559 --> 00:20:21,400
But,

375
00:20:22,319 --> 00:20:23,759
won't this hurt the acquisition?

376
00:20:24,200 --> 00:20:26,039
if Lysen Group loses
to Yinyu Technology,

377
00:20:26,799 --> 00:20:27,880
Jiang Dongchao,

378
00:20:28,690 --> 00:20:29,880
will bear the responsibility.

379
00:20:30,759 --> 00:20:32,240
So what you're saying is

380
00:20:34,200 --> 00:20:35,920
now is the perfect time

381
00:20:36,160 --> 00:20:37,960
to force Mr. Jiang out of Lysen Group?

382
00:20:39,200 --> 00:20:40,160
For you,

383
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,680
this is the chance of a lifetime.

384
00:20:48,160 --> 00:20:49,319
Forgive me, Mr. Li.

385
00:20:49,800 --> 00:20:51,319
Whether Mr. Jiang stays at Lysen Group

386
00:20:51,319 --> 00:20:52,440
is of no interest to me.

387
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:54,750
I have no desire to get involved.

388
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,720
Miss Rao,

389
00:20:57,720 --> 00:21:01,039
you've been in the middle
of this for a long time.

390
00:21:01,440 --> 00:21:03,440
Everything is interconnected.

391
00:21:04,319 --> 00:21:05,480
Think about it carefully.

392
00:21:06,599 --> 00:21:09,000
If Jiang Dongchao stays,

393
00:21:09,880 --> 00:21:11,319
given his business philosophy,

394
00:21:11,400 --> 00:21:12,440
do you think the projects

395
00:21:12,440 --> 00:21:13,920
you and Yu Peidong value

396
00:21:14,319 --> 00:21:16,039
will ever see the light of day?

397
00:21:30,240 --> 00:21:31,039
Mr. Li.

398
00:21:31,359 --> 00:21:32,160
Actually,

399
00:21:32,640 --> 00:21:34,039
we're on the exact same page.

400
00:21:34,839 --> 00:21:35,839
I completely understand

401
00:21:35,839 --> 00:21:36,960
why you had to make

402
00:21:37,599 --> 00:21:38,880
this difficult decision.

403
00:21:40,240 --> 00:21:41,200
In fact, I know

404
00:21:43,200 --> 00:21:44,559
you did it to protect me.

405
00:21:46,599 --> 00:21:47,640
But don't you worry.

406
00:21:48,480 --> 00:21:49,279
As of now,

407
00:21:50,359 --> 00:21:51,720
everything has been handled.

408
00:21:53,359 --> 00:21:55,039
I've already allied with Baiye Group.

409
00:21:57,000 --> 00:21:57,960
The takeover of Bosi

410
00:22:00,960 --> 00:22:01,960
is already a done deal.

411
00:22:11,000 --> 00:22:12,160
(Rao Yuci engineered)

412
00:22:12,160 --> 00:22:13,359
(all of this.)

413
00:22:13,519 --> 00:22:15,400
(You were part of her plan, too.)

414
00:22:16,319 --> 00:22:17,519
(You're nothing more than)

415
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,799
(another pawn being played.)

416
00:22:28,200 --> 00:22:29,000
Yuci.

417
00:22:29,839 --> 00:22:31,060
After you finish work tonight,

418
00:22:31,240 --> 00:22:32,440
come to my office.

419
00:22:51,720 --> 00:22:53,079
Here, Chen.

420
00:22:55,200 --> 00:22:57,160
Do I add this now?

421
00:22:57,160 --> 00:22:57,799
No.

422
00:22:58,799 --> 00:22:59,640
Wait a bit longer.

423
00:23:00,400 --> 00:23:01,240
Don't be nervous.

424
00:23:02,519 --> 00:23:04,260
I wanted to bake
this birthday cake myself

425
00:23:04,400 --> 00:23:05,880
to give Yuci a surprise.

426
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:07,160
I just hope I don't mess it up.

427
00:23:07,279 --> 00:23:08,079
It's fine.

428
00:23:08,519 --> 00:23:09,759
Even if it's not perfect,

429
00:23:10,079 --> 00:23:11,839
Yuci will still be thrilled.

430
00:23:12,279 --> 00:23:13,319
You know girls.

431
00:23:13,480 --> 00:23:14,880
They just love it when a guy

432
00:23:15,039 --> 00:23:16,279
actually puts in the effort.

433
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:21,519
Yes, you...

434
00:23:21,720 --> 00:23:22,319
Oh! Sorry.

435
00:23:22,319 --> 00:23:22,920
It's okay.

436
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:23,599
My bad.

437
00:23:23,599 --> 00:23:24,930
Don't worry about it. I'll get it.

438
00:23:41,039 --> 00:23:41,839
Miss Rao.

439
00:23:41,960 --> 00:23:43,599
Mr. Jiang is waiting for you inside.

440
00:23:43,599 --> 00:23:44,480
I'm heading off now.

441
00:23:44,480 --> 00:23:45,119
Goodnight.

442
00:23:51,400 --> 00:23:52,200
Come in.

443
00:23:57,920 --> 00:23:59,200
Mr. Jiang, you wanted to see me?

444
00:24:10,920 --> 00:24:11,960
Everyone's gone.

445
00:24:12,480 --> 00:24:13,279
They've all left.

446
00:24:15,200 --> 00:24:16,000
Yuci.

447
00:24:16,640 --> 00:24:17,759
Since your return,

448
00:24:17,799 --> 00:24:19,400
you haven't stopped for a single breath.

449
00:24:19,839 --> 00:24:20,640
You've been

450
00:24:23,240 --> 00:24:24,039
working too hard.

451
00:24:26,799 --> 00:24:28,440
I've always admired your courage.

452
00:24:29,559 --> 00:24:30,920
I told you before...

453
00:24:36,759 --> 00:24:37,680
The road up the mountain

454
00:24:38,170 --> 00:24:39,400
is one you must walk yourself.

455
00:24:39,780 --> 00:24:41,400
That's the only way
to find your footing.

456
00:24:42,079 --> 00:24:43,279
Your idealism

457
00:24:44,759 --> 00:24:46,359
makes you feel invincible.

458
00:24:47,160 --> 00:24:48,180
That's all well and good.

459
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,000
But haven't you noticed?

460
00:24:50,240 --> 00:24:51,160
Sometimes,

461
00:24:51,640 --> 00:24:53,440
it makes you incredibly conceited.

462
00:24:54,119 --> 00:24:55,720
And the downside of that conceit

463
00:24:55,839 --> 00:24:56,960
is that you think

464
00:24:57,519 --> 00:25:00,039
you can provoke just anyone.

465
00:25:02,680 --> 00:25:03,759
Enough.

466
00:25:04,680 --> 00:25:06,119
That's enough of the pleasantries.

467
00:25:07,680 --> 00:25:08,480
Now,

468
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:11,680
it's time to settle our accounts.

469
00:25:35,160 --> 00:25:36,000
Rao Yuci.

470
00:25:37,400 --> 00:25:38,440
Do you think fate

471
00:25:39,200 --> 00:25:41,039
is playing a joke on us?

472
00:25:45,220 --> 00:25:48,540
(Chen Mo)

473
00:25:52,220 --> 00:25:55,860
(Rao Yuci)

474
00:26:15,079 --> 00:26:15,880
Does it hurt?

475
00:26:18,920 --> 00:26:20,759
Remember what you did to me?

476
00:26:21,200 --> 00:26:23,160
I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

477
00:26:25,319 --> 00:26:27,480
I don't want your apologies.

478
00:26:29,079 --> 00:26:30,319
I don't want to hear it.

479
00:26:30,640 --> 00:26:31,559
No!

480
00:26:34,319 --> 00:26:35,759
You were the one who reminded me

481
00:26:36,880 --> 00:26:38,519
that we are exactly the same.

482
00:26:40,400 --> 00:26:42,079
The answers you'll never find

483
00:26:43,079 --> 00:26:44,559
and the love you'll never have

484
00:26:45,680 --> 00:26:47,640
are where your deepest pain lies.

485
00:26:48,759 --> 00:26:49,519
I've been searching

486
00:26:49,519 --> 00:26:50,799
for answers about my father.

487
00:26:52,480 --> 00:26:53,839
Aren't you doing the same?

488
00:26:54,880 --> 00:26:56,400
Haven't you always wondered

489
00:26:57,400 --> 00:26:58,400
why Rao Shusheng

490
00:26:58,920 --> 00:27:00,680
loathed you so much?

491
00:27:07,720 --> 00:27:08,930
There are things from the past

492
00:27:11,240 --> 00:27:12,480
that you should learn now.

493
00:27:13,700 --> 00:27:16,780
(Three Years Ago)

494
00:27:17,680 --> 00:27:18,480
Mr. Rao.

495
00:27:18,720 --> 00:27:20,119
I've prepared all the paperwork

496
00:27:20,119 --> 00:27:21,400
for Yuci's admission.

497
00:27:21,759 --> 00:27:23,720
I've already signed
the representative agreement.

498
00:27:24,519 --> 00:27:25,680
Thank you, Liangliang.

499
00:27:25,700 --> 00:27:27,079
Just leave it in the study for me.

500
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:43,359
(Rao Yuci.)

501
00:27:44,359 --> 00:27:45,200
(You were originally)

502
00:27:45,200 --> 00:27:46,759
(supposed to have a sibling.)

503
00:27:48,000 --> 00:27:48,799
(But,)

504
00:27:50,240 --> 00:27:52,359
(while you were in your mother's womb,)

505
00:27:52,680 --> 00:27:54,519
(you absorbed the other embryo.)

506
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:58,000
(This is what I read)

507
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,960
(in your dad's diary.)

508
00:28:03,400 --> 00:28:04,680
(Your birth)

509
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:08,039
(brought only misery to your family.)

510
00:28:08,160 --> 00:28:09,279
(You lived,)

511
00:28:10,240 --> 00:28:13,240
(but your father lost his other child.)

512
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:19,000
(Every time he looks at you,
he is reminded of that child.)

513
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:29,599
(Operating Room)

514
00:28:29,599 --> 00:28:31,319
Congratulations! It's a girl.

515
00:28:35,799 --> 00:28:37,079
(That birthmark)

516
00:28:37,480 --> 00:28:38,920
(is the mark that child)

517
00:28:38,920 --> 00:28:40,720
(left branded upon you.)

518
00:28:43,279 --> 00:28:44,599
Have you ever considered

519
00:28:46,240 --> 00:28:47,880
that all of your father's pain

520
00:28:47,880 --> 00:28:48,920
came from you?

521
00:28:58,359 --> 00:28:59,160
Hello?

522
00:28:59,200 --> 00:29:00,160
Hello, Shusheng?

523
00:29:01,150 --> 00:29:02,400
You need to come home right now.

524
00:29:02,400 --> 00:29:03,820
Your mother isn't going to make it.

525
00:29:15,559 --> 00:29:16,440
That's why no one

526
00:29:16,440 --> 00:29:18,240
can ever truly get close to you.

527
00:29:19,079 --> 00:29:19,880
And you will

528
00:29:21,799 --> 00:29:23,480
only ever find one answer.

529
00:29:28,559 --> 00:29:29,920
You are destined

530
00:29:32,519 --> 00:29:34,640
to never be loved by anyone.

531
00:29:34,640 --> 00:29:37,580
♪With blood♪

532
00:29:37,580 --> 00:29:41,260
♪From the start to the end
you're damned♪

533
00:29:41,260 --> 00:29:45,300
♪I'm coming back survived♪

534
00:29:45,300 --> 00:29:49,020
♪Feeling great to see you fall♪

535
00:29:49,020 --> 00:29:53,420
♪I'm taking back what' s mine♪

536
00:29:53,420 --> 00:29:59,220
♪Bringing horror to the battlefield♪

537
00:30:03,599 --> 00:30:04,640
Every time, you use

538
00:30:04,640 --> 00:30:05,960
idealism as a front

539
00:30:06,519 --> 00:30:07,680
to help people.

540
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:09,920
But have you ever considered

541
00:30:10,839 --> 00:30:12,440
that all the hardships they face

542
00:30:12,559 --> 00:30:13,319
were caused

543
00:30:13,319 --> 00:30:14,839
by those same ideals of yours?

544
00:30:18,599 --> 00:30:20,279
Stop using your so-called "nobility"

545
00:30:21,400 --> 00:30:22,559
to deceive people.

546
00:30:29,680 --> 00:30:32,079
Dongchao, you were a bit too rough.

547
00:30:36,759 --> 00:30:38,319
I've been looking forward

548
00:30:38,559 --> 00:30:40,319
to this moment for a long time.

549
00:30:41,039 --> 00:30:41,920
Rao Yuci.

550
00:30:43,920 --> 00:30:45,440
I wanted to see for myself

551
00:30:46,240 --> 00:30:48,240
if you were capable of feeling afraid.

552
00:30:49,319 --> 00:30:50,960
You're terrified, aren't you?

553
00:30:52,079 --> 00:30:53,000
Just like the way you

554
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:54,680
drove our Muran to his death.

555
00:30:56,759 --> 00:30:57,559
They say

556
00:30:59,319 --> 00:31:01,839
everyone must face

557
00:31:01,839 --> 00:31:03,119
consequences for their actions.

558
00:31:06,200 --> 00:31:08,039
I think that's just an empty phrase.

559
00:31:09,440 --> 00:31:10,279
Just like you.

560
00:31:11,279 --> 00:31:15,000
You two girls and your little squabbles
right here

561
00:31:15,119 --> 00:31:16,839
left us with no peace at all.

562
00:31:20,240 --> 00:31:21,960
You thought that four percent

563
00:31:22,960 --> 00:31:24,400
could sway the outcome?

564
00:31:25,039 --> 00:31:26,559
That it would be the winning move?

565
00:31:28,720 --> 00:31:30,839
You really are naive.

566
00:31:33,799 --> 00:31:34,880
The game of capital

567
00:31:34,880 --> 00:31:36,640
is no place for children.

568
00:31:38,519 --> 00:31:41,000
As long as I join forces
with Jiang Dongchao,

569
00:31:41,240 --> 00:31:42,960
added to Yang Jinwan's shares,

570
00:31:42,960 --> 00:31:44,839
your pathetic four percent

571
00:31:44,839 --> 00:31:46,920
won't even make a ripple.

572
00:31:48,039 --> 00:31:50,039
Don't be so full of yourself.

573
00:31:54,880 --> 00:31:56,039
Go ahead, call the police.

574
00:31:59,680 --> 00:32:00,720
You can do it right now.

575
00:32:02,100 --> 00:32:03,700
(Chen Mo)

576
00:32:05,240 --> 00:32:06,400
But don't forget,

577
00:32:06,920 --> 00:32:07,880
you still have Chen Mo,

578
00:32:08,519 --> 00:32:09,319
Yu Peidong,

579
00:32:09,480 --> 00:32:10,839
all of Investment Dept 3,

580
00:32:11,200 --> 00:32:12,240
and your parents.

581
00:32:13,079 --> 00:32:14,599
Maybe you don't care about them,

582
00:32:15,079 --> 00:32:15,960
or that mute person's

583
00:32:15,960 --> 00:32:16,920
shabby little shop.

584
00:32:17,640 --> 00:32:18,759
I will deal with them,

585
00:32:18,759 --> 00:32:19,799
one by one.

586
00:32:20,160 --> 00:32:20,960
No matter

587
00:32:20,960 --> 00:32:21,920
where I stand,

588
00:32:22,759 --> 00:32:23,839
I can make it happen.

589
00:32:27,279 --> 00:32:28,839
Consider today a warning.

590
00:32:30,119 --> 00:32:30,960
There are things

591
00:32:32,039 --> 00:32:32,839
you shouldn't touch.

592
00:32:34,079 --> 00:32:34,920
There are people

593
00:32:35,599 --> 00:32:36,960
you should never anger.

594
00:32:38,519 --> 00:32:39,319
Do you understand?

595
00:32:46,119 --> 00:32:46,920
Rao Yuci.

596
00:32:47,039 --> 00:32:48,440
Aren't you quite the strategist?

597
00:32:49,519 --> 00:32:50,839
But in today's "strategy",

598
00:32:50,880 --> 00:32:53,000
the three of us have just witnessed

599
00:32:53,000 --> 00:32:54,559
your emotional instability

600
00:32:54,720 --> 00:32:56,039
and your psychotic episode.

601
00:33:18,200 --> 00:33:19,000
Mrs. Rao.

602
00:33:19,200 --> 00:33:20,640
I'll check on Yuci at the office.

603
00:33:20,759 --> 00:33:21,559
Alright.

604
00:33:22,620 --> 00:33:23,780
(Dr. Zhai)

605
00:33:24,920 --> 00:33:25,720
Wait.

606
00:33:26,920 --> 00:33:27,720
Hello?

607
00:33:34,799 --> 00:33:36,440
Yuci's father is awake.

608
00:33:53,140 --> 00:33:56,900
=Episode 22=
(Branded)

609
00:33:57,461 --> 00:33:59,901
(All animals in this production
were treated humanely)

610
00:33:59,901 --> 00:34:06,101
♪Take a breath and swallow
the words you couldn't say♪

611
00:34:06,861 --> 00:34:10,061
♪No need to force your heart anymore♪

612
00:34:10,061 --> 00:34:14,581
♪Searching for the season
we once missed♪

613
00:34:14,581 --> 00:34:22,101
♪Leave this place,
though wounded still stay strong♪

614
00:34:22,101 --> 00:34:26,021
♪You must believe
one day the rain will fall♪

615
00:34:26,021 --> 00:34:30,061
♪And wash away the mud
that stains your soul♪

616
00:34:30,061 --> 00:34:33,581
♪Find your freedom in the wild♪

617
00:34:33,581 --> 00:34:37,541
♪Take your stride and move ahead♪

618
00:34:37,541 --> 00:34:41,701
♪I will stay behind
and wait for your eyes♪

619
00:34:41,701 --> 00:34:45,901
♪To rebuild
the same flesh and soul again♪

620
00:34:45,901 --> 00:34:49,701
♪Wander freely through the thorns♪

621
00:34:49,701 --> 00:34:53,781
♪Keep walking through the light♪

622
00:34:53,781 --> 00:34:57,981
♪Fate is absurd, don't stop for anyone♪

623
00:34:57,981 --> 00:35:04,301
♪What you dare to lose
will one day be your own♪

624
00:35:21,421 --> 00:35:28,061
♪I'm sorry, I still owe you these words♪

625
00:35:28,061 --> 00:35:31,901
♪An apology that came too late♪

626
00:35:31,901 --> 00:35:36,541
♪Yet it's also the path
that saves my soul♪

627
00:35:36,621 --> 00:35:44,021
♪When the cold wind
passes it takes the past away♪

628
00:35:44,021 --> 00:35:48,101
♪You must believe and stand unwavering♪

629
00:35:48,101 --> 00:35:52,181
♪There will be hands
to pull you from the deep♪

630
00:35:52,181 --> 00:35:56,181
♪Find your freedom in the silence♪

631
00:35:56,181 --> 00:35:59,941
♪Let your wounds be mended♪

632
00:35:59,941 --> 00:36:04,141
♪Gray is not the past
and pain is not a shame♪

633
00:36:04,141 --> 00:36:08,301
♪Sometimes the sunlight
makes the world look crueler♪

634
00:36:08,301 --> 00:36:12,021
♪Wander through the echoes of regret♪

635
00:36:12,021 --> 00:36:16,061
♪Be forgiven and be sheltered♪

636
00:36:16,061 --> 00:36:20,101
♪After everything shatters,
hold my hand♪

637
00:36:20,101 --> 00:36:26,301
♪A flower reborn
will finally bloom forever♪
